26 March 2014Deputy President Kgalema Motlanthe will meet with stakeholders from the mining industry for a regularly scheduled consultative forum aimed at bringing stability to the sector.Media are invited to a media briefing post the meeting, the details are as follows:Date: Thursday, 27 March 2014 Time: 12h00 Venue: Sefako Makgatho Presidential Guesthouse Media are advised to submit their names, ID numbers and designation to Mbalenhle Nkomo at mbalenhle@po.gov.za or 071 487 2379 by 9h00am tomorrow. Media will be required to present their press cards.Issued by Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)